<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend_View_Helper_Action has no exception Handling.  If an exception is thrown in the action, and caught - the view renderer object never gets set back into place.</p>

<p>I wrote a little patch around the issue - it just catches the exception in the dispatch, and throws the same exception after setting the view stuff back to the original state.</p>

